graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|container platform| K8s[Kubernetes / OpenShift 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine<br/>DSP v2 default| Argo[Argo Workflows 3.5.14]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine<br/>DSP v1 legacy| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+]
    DSPO -->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth v4.12+]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage<br/>required| S3[S3-compatible Storage]
    DSPO -->|metadata storage<br/>required| Database[MySQL/MariaDB 10.3+]
    DSPO -->|container images| Registry[Container Registry]

    %% Optional External Dependencies
    DSPO -.->|optional mTLS<br/>MLMD proxy| Envoy[Envoy Proxy<br/>OSSM 2.x]
    DSPO -.->|optional TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSPO -->|external access| Route[OpenShift Route]
    DSPO -.->|optional service mesh| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio]
    DSPO -->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Integration Points
    DSPO -->|model serving| KServe[KServe]
    DSPO -->|distributed compute| Ray[Ray]
    DSPO -.->|can deploy to| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]

    %% Bidirectional integrations
    Dashboard -->|embeds UI| DSPO
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|uses| DSPO

    %% Storage alternatives
    S3 -.->|OR production| ExternalS3[External S3<br/>AWS/compatible]
    S3 -.->|OR dev/test| Minio[Minio<br/>deployed by DSPO]
    Database -.->|OR production| ExternalDB[External MySQL/MariaDB]
    Database -.->|OR deployed| MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>deployed by DSPO]

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Argo fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Tekton fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OAuth fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Registry fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Envoy fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333

    %% Storage
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Database fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ExternalS3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Minio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ExternalDB fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style MariaDB fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333

    %% Internal ODH
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Route fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ServiceMesh fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Integrations
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Ray fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ModelMesh fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
